Package cardgame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardGame
    This CardGame class is used to launch the GUI elements of the FXMLDocument which is the first scene of the program
    ConfirmBoxController
    This ConfirmBoxController class is used to determine which interface should be displayed after players clicked 'yes' or 'no'
    FourPlayerMode
    This FourPlayerMode class is used to manage labels and buttons of the Interface and act as main function of the Game Class
    FXMLDocumentController
    This FXMLDocumentController class is used to load the GUI element for the scene 'FourPlayerMode'
    Game
    This Game class is used to create all necessary function involved during the game
